      <PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt>To use education, research, and activist training to help the American people understand how to add an amendment to the Constitution of the United States that will restore free and fair elections, and why doing so is crucial to the future of our nation. Consistent with this purpose, Wolf-PAC Action Fund releases donor information on its website far beyond that required in this public disclosure.</PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt>
